M712LUin wrote a review Feb 2024
Seoul, South Korea2 contributions
Amazing
I used the club lounge and all the staff here were very friendly. I am especially grateful to Steven, Jadon, Lucas, who was very impressive. And I caught a cold during my stay here, and the staff took good care of me and called a doctor, so I was able to recover during my stay. I stayed here twice and it was so good that I came with my husband after getting married. It just happened to be my husband's birthday and he made unforgettable memories. All the staff were really nice, but the memorable staff was Maximus, and the male staff with silver glasses who worked in the club lounge during the day from the morning of February 8th. Thank you for your visit again next time.
Read more
Date of stay: February 2024
