A Perfect Evening at InterContinental Danang: A Special Thanks to Ms. Ly Pham
This marks my third visit to the Long Bar restaurant within a year, as I make it a point to dine here each time I stay at the InterContinental Danang. I've always been fond of its ambiance and food. However, this time, in addition to the aforementioned qualities, I particularly want to extend my gratitude to Ms. Ly Pham. She assisted us during our meal at Long Bar and showcased exceptional professionalism, including impeccable table manners, the sequence of serving tea and wine, and positioning. Her attentive and thoughtful service impressed both my family and me greatly, contributing to a truly perfect evening at Long Bar.
